title: Family Tree Maker v7.0
description:
Family Tree Maker 7.0
*********************

Older but good and fully functional version of a popular family tree and genealogy program. 

.daa format

Instructions:
- Extract file with WinRAR or similar program.
- Open file with PowerISO (if you don't have it search for a torrent).
- Burn to a blank CD.
- Install program on computer with burnt disc.

PLEASE SEED. This means leaving the torrent active after you have finished downloading and not removing it from your torrent client. This allows others a better chance to download the complete file. Thanks.
